  "replies_posted": [
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/UnderdogNBA/status/2034662430597612010",
      "reply_text": "Lottery order is always a crapshoot. Anything can happen.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:23:05.122360+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LALMuse/status/2034662746063548780",
      "reply_text": "That's a tough ask. He's been cold from deep lately.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:23:40.566877+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/The_BBall_Index/status/2034661172281295067",
      "reply_text": "SA's shooting is insane. No surprise he tops this list.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:24:47.907304+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Cavs_Enthusiast/status/2034661606966075633",
      "reply_text": "You think the Bulls are a tough matchup. They've been playing some solid D lately",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:25:22.501143+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Basket_Infos/status/2034661298089210013",
      "reply_text": "Good for him, but Parish's record is still a big deal. Respect to the Chief for acknowledging it.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:26:15.680079+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBA__Courtside/status/2034641462923522219",
      "reply_text": "Yeah Bron's presence can change a series, but Luka's a whole different story. He's a top 3 player in the league.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:36:16.786385+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/30problemz/status/2034647961569763667",
      "reply_text": "That 65-game rule is a game-changer. No more one-man shows.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:37:00.780050+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Underdog/status/2034646082332856781",
      "reply_text": "Not surprised. Brice Sensabaugh has had some big games this season.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:37:39.815651+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/RapsShowYo/status/2034661927171813388",
      "reply_text": "Still hurts to this day",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:38:33.294534+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/HarbeardJames/status/2034662656133701844",
      "reply_text": "Giannis has been carrying a lot of weight for this team",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:39:13.760219+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/wipetheratteeth/status/2034649403898888620",
      "reply_text": "That's a strong take. Luka's dominance is undeniable.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:39:47.466119+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/raptorsrepublic/status/2034662003403358372",
      "reply_text": "Not sure about that. What makes him the X factor?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:40:40.928881+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/statdefender/status/2034640257669312866",
      "reply_text": "Luka's drawing fouls at an insane rate this season",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:41:27.428530+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/MavsPR/status/2034658880379097421",
      "reply_text": "G League assignment for AJ Johnson",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:42:05.700691+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Thechat101/status/2034672542342914436",
      "reply_text": "That's the Lakers I've been waiting to see all season. Defense is finally clicking.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:53:26.155299+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BrasilAD/status/2034672511498019143",
      "reply_text": "Impressive. Shows he's still got it.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:54:10.445163+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheChefKayy/status/2034669289924686302",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, a sweep would've been huge momentum. Still a solid week overall though.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:55:01.398064+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NoCeilingsNBA/status/2034666920289673667",
      "reply_text": "That's a bold claim. What makes Flemings the next 'King'?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:55:36.222795+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBABlackburn/status/2034638522708332625",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, Jokic's TOVs are a concern. He's got to find a way to manage that.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:56:15.201474+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ShammyPlayz/status/2034641792394531140",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, Booker's been consistent without Brooks. His usage is up",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:56:57.404679+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/StephenPG3/status/2034646638388793450",
      "reply_text": "4 weeks in, still not seeing the shot fall for him consistently",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T16:57:44.982362+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheAthleticNBA/status/2034646183524593935",
      "reply_text": "Reminds me of the excitement he brought to the draft process last year. Same energy now.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T17:07:47.981236+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/primenic_eth/status/2034674939400196225",
      "reply_text": "Yeah Stephon Castle's been on a roll. But what about his defense?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T17:08:22.898290+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NickFeddyy/status/2034649413684023562",
      "reply_text": "Some big names on this list. Luka's range is always a concern for defenses.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T17:09:12.781408+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/KenHeLive/status/2034661159291220161",
      "reply_text": "Yeah that's true. Durant's been pretty open about his role on the team.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T17:09:56.006859+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheAthletic/status/2034646282002690290",
      "reply_text": "Yeah that's the vibe. He's already making a difference",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T17:10:32.612293+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBA/status/2034676278087803267",
      "reply_text": "Big milestone for King James",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T17:21:08.164623+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/djones8301/status/2034638467083161713",
      "reply_text": "Defense matters more than shooting in the paint. They can't guard anyone.",
